result.formatted_address: 441號 Castle Peak Rd, Cheung Sha Wan, Hong Kong
result.name: Gingko Moment

reviews.text:
Happy moments with oldies song accompanied by guitar and solo singer. Food is normal and not much surprise. A bit too dry and over cooked with those meat. But services from their staffs were very friendly and caring. 
Whatever, who loves to spend times with good old friends is a nice place to choose.

Tried once at quarry bay branch, it was good so when I knew there is one here then must try!

Came here for lunch, didn’t reserve a table and it was so crowded! Luckily there was a table (there were two ppl came one minute later and they didn’t get a table!)

Ordered chicken steak and pork chop and it was so good! Especially the pork chop with apple sauce!!!

Love that and will definitely come back again.
Nice food and good service, wonderful restaurant with live music and songs.
Food is above average with good quality yet service provided is of heart warming.
Quite good and reasonable price, support the elderly!

result.name: 銀杏館 銀杏時光

reviews.text:
抵食，又好食，又可支持社企，協助長者就業。

半自助午餐的沙律菜好新鮮，而且任食，當日餐廳紅菜頭湯，美味又健康。

預先訂枱有餐飲送。👍

主菜意粉十分大碟，食咗一碟沙律菜的我都有點飽，意粉味道很好只係最終勉強食埋佢免得浪費。

食物出品絶對係第一等評，但服務亦相當重要。
今晚兩者同時出現，多謝Patrick的見意。
食物唔錯，有歌聽氣氛好，值得支持的社企
很有意義的社企，食物主調夠健康，推薦。
